l late-medieval text.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 4aManchester Digital Textbooks. 7aHISTORY / Medieval.2bisacsh  aHeinrich Institoris.  aJakob Sprenger.  ainquisitors.  amalleus maleficarum.  amedieval history.  atheology.  awitchcraft.1 aMaxwell-Stuart, P.G., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMaxwell-Stuart, Peter, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt40uhttps://doi.org/10.7765/978152615358640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781526153586423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781526153586/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles